import numpy as np
import lcapy as lcp
from lcapy import t, s
from lcapy.discretetime import n, z       # Pacote localizado em https://pypi.org/project/lcapy/
                                          # e documentao em https://lcapy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
import control as ctrl               
import math
import cmath
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline
plt.rcParams.update({'figure.figsize':[16,9],
                     'font.size': 22, 
                     'xaxis.labellocation': 'right',
                     'yaxis.labellocation': 'top'})

def tf_control_2_lcapy(tf):
    tfout = 0;
    temp = 0;
     
    num = tf.num[0][0];
    den = tf.den[0][0];
    
    if ctrl.isctime(tf):
        for i in range(len(num)):
            tfout += num[i]*(s**(len(num)-1-i));
        
        for i in range(len(den)):
            temp += den[i]*(s**(len(den)-1-i));
        tfout /= temp;
    else:
        for i in range(len(num)):
            tfout += num[i]*(z**(len(num)-1-i));
        
        for i in range(len(den)):
            temp += den[i]*(z**(len(den)-1-i));
        tfout /= temp;
            
    return tfout;

In [15]:
# Tempo de acomodao para 5%
ts = [None]*2;

delta = lambda x: abs((x[-1]-x)/x[-1]);
absolute_difference = lambda x, idx, percentage: abs(x[idx]-x[-1]-percentage*x[-1]);

# Tempo de acomodao de 5% para resposta 'contnua':
idx = np.argwhere(delta(yout) > 0.05)[-1][0];
if absolute_difference(yout,idx,0.05) < absolute_difference(yout,idx+1,0.05):
    ts[0] = t[idx];
else:
    ts[0] = t[idx+1];
    
print("Tempo de acomodao para 5% da resposta contnua:");
print("\tTs (5%) = \n\t", ts[0], 's\n');

# Tempo de acomodao de 5% para resposta discreta:
idx = np.argwhere(delta(y) > 0.05)[-1][0];
if absolute_difference(y,idx,0.05) < absolute_difference(y,idx+1,0.05):
    ts[1] = k[idx];
else:
    ts[1] = k[idx+1];
    
print("Tempo de acomodao para 5% da resposta discreta:");
print("\tTs (5%) = \n\t", ts[1], 's\n');

e0 = C.num[0][0][0];
e1 = C.num[0][0][1];
e2 = C.num[0][0][2];
u1_bloco_C = -C.den[0][0][1];
u2_bloco_C = -C.den[0][0][2];

u[i] = e0*e[i] + e1*e[i-1] + u1_bloco_C*u[i-1];

k = np.linspace(0, tfinal, Kmax);
r = 1.5*np.heaviside(1,k);
e = np.zeros_like(k);
u = np.zeros_like(k);
y = np.zeros_like(k);

e0 = C.num[0][0][0];
e1 = C.num[0][0][1];
e2 = C.num[0][0][2];
u1_bloco_C = -C.den[0][0][1];
u2_bloco_C = -C.den[0][0][2];
u0_bloco_G = Gz.num[0][0][0];
u1_bloco_G = Gz.num[0][0][1];
y1 = -Gz.den[0][0][1];
y2 = -Gz.den[0][0][2];

i = 0;
e[i] = r[i];
u[i] = e0*e[i];

i = 1;
y[i] = u0_bloco_G*u[i-1] + y1*y[i-1];
e[i] = r[i] - y[i];
u[i] = e0*e[i] + e1*e[i-1] + u1_bloco_C*u[i-1];

for i in range(2, Kmax):
    y[i] = u0_bloco_G*u[i-1] + u1_bloco_G*u[i-2] + y1*y[i-1] + y2*y[i-2];
    e[i] = r[i] - y[i];
    u[i] = e0*e[i] + e1*e[i-1] + e2*e[i-2] + u1_bloco_C*u[i-1] + u2_bloco_C*u[i-2];

yFTMF2 = ctrl.step_response(1.5*FTMF2, k)[1];
    
plt.figure();
plt.plot(k, yFTMF2, ds='steps-post');
plt.plot(k, yFTMF2, 'r*', markersize=20);
plt.plot(k, y, 'ko', markerfacecolor='None', markersize=20);
plt.title("Resposta do sistema para uma entrada do tipo degrau unitrio");
plt.xlabel("$kT$");
plt.ylabel("$y \, (kT)$");
plt.grid();
plt.tight_layout();
plt.show();
